Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术是将物质理解分解并且再构筑的科学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不是万能的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不能从无中诞生物质
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想要得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必须付出相应的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也就是炼金术的基本 等价交换
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师有一个禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是任何人都不能侵犯的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:04.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯·休斯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被身上纹了咬尾蛇刺青的神秘人物杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马斯坦古对这一血案怀有疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了这件事和军队上层部有关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次决意进入中央
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不知道的爱德和阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与温莉一起向着师傅所在的城市达普利斯前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向着南部开始了旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}拉修巴雷的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉修巴雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葛斯的11年式造型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到有一天能亲眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是机械铠的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没理由非得在这大热天里观赏机械铠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扔下温莉早点去达普利斯就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小弟 打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个机械铠的形状很稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的哦 大家也都来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等一下 住手 住…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 那里 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都热心于研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 所以才说机械铠技师这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家炼金术师的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一定是帕妮娘干的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕妮娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专找观光客下手的小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道那家伙现在在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 相对地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让我们看一下小哥的机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在一个叫多明尼克的机械铠技师那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说为了能采掘优质的矿石而住在深山里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条路真的是对的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被骗了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追根究底 还不是因为你想去那个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银怀表被偷是因为你自己不注意吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 你们俩看下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真会到处躲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 呼吸变急促了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 还给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西在这里并不稀奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左脚是1.5英吋加尔巴林炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来抓我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不会让你逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别放她走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 绝对不放开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,750)}（捏紧）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在让我仔细看清楚之前是绝对不放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕妮娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 请放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种机械铠 第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说悬挂装置也很高级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但怎么看 这个全体的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这没有多余的设计
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说是艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我的银怀表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做出这种机械铠 我真的很佩服你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个不是我制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得有点重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.65,0:07:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给装备者加上负担可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这小子才那么矮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说我矮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 弄得再轻一点的话 我的身高也会长高？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 好高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身高好高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们真矮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多明尼克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请收我为弟子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微想一想也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 我不收弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您就教她如何做出能让我长高的机械铠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 爸爸很顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水蚤 水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 是小宝宝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能摸摸你的肚子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以前也像这样呆在妈妈的肚子里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气不好 关节就痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么装上了机械铠？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.99,0:09:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为被卷进列车事故
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双亲都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有可以依靠的人 再加上不能走路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉就像是世界末日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那个时候 遇到了多明尼克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一副自己是这个世上最不幸的人似的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种人最让人生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死人的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我的表情一定很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 莫名其妙地就被装上了机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手术痛死了 恢复训练辛苦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用双脚站在大地上的时候 我非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很感谢多明尼克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算花费一生来报答他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还一次都没有收过我钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才 偷窃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要感谢他的话 就不要再偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个双脚是多明尼克先生的诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你也必须用诚意来报答他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说要用一生来报答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不要偷窃 实实在在地站起来工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你那双脚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样 多明尼克先生也一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏踏实实地工作来还这个情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 要去还了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 难道弄坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖子打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是用炼金术把盖子盖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是显然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为里面有被看到了就会很害臊的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来看看爱德的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“别忘了 11年10月3日”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个还给爱德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求多明尼克先生收我为弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马 马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上要生了 莎特拉太太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么大的雨 没法带去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑一趟把医生叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸马上就会把医生带来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再忍耐一下 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说忍… 但是要生的时候还是会生出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么 听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要生了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 没有医生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们自己来做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 有接生的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 也没有犹豫的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家协力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来接生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德和阿尔去烧热水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕妮娘把所有的毛巾找来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 理多尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有消毒用的酒精
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仓库里应该有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 把饮用水放在莎特拉太太的枕边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她来做不会有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是在医生之家出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小就把家里的医学书当画册一样看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说 没有真正学过？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计只是记得一个大概的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在只有依靠她的知识和胆量了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧开水 消毒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起来 快想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕妮娘 你进来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.49,0:15:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键的时候 我是多么地无力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛 痛 痛 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（怕 怕 怕）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说不存在神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有现在 拜托他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血 血…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出 出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 真的出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 厉害 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 厉害地叫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就只有那种小孩子一样的感想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 这可是生命的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师研究了几百年还没有成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类制造人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把生命的神秘和炼金术做比较
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 是我的职业病
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 孩子平安地出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后还有要我做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我拉起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（腰软了）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让比自己矮的男孩子背 真是耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说就把你扔地上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我偷看了银怀表里的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强行打开的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都没让阿尔看过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对自己的警告和觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还真是没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的事情 必须要用这种形式带在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是你在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不能回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是你在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们兄弟俩都不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我代替你们哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是回乡下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆一个人会寂寞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为看到了爱德的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不能只抱着半吊子的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不需要连你也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要进一步加强自己的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你用上更好的机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了爱德能安心地继续旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我再次去求多明尼克先生收我为弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.42,0:20:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理多尔先生想让你过去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕妮娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 快点把怀表还给我 你这小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不需要用右手打我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用左手再打一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爷爷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:39.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角色完全变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（娇宠 娇宠）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母子的健康状况良好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产后的处理也很适当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接生这种事 连大人也会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我已经拚命了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是受大伙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么郑重的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没招了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（灵机一动）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 现在就收个弟子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个和那个是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不收弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无论如何都想做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以给你介绍一个住在山脚下的好技师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔来参观你的工作 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔来看看我的孙子 那倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的野丫头也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错过这班的话 下趟去达普利斯的就是三天后了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.35,0:21:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万事小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要给婆婆打电话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想被你说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好偷学那个老头子的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见面的时候给我装个更好的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在师傅居住的城市 达普利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年们回想起修行的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是走向真理的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.95,0:24:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.51,0:24:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第12话 一即是全 全即是一
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.26,0:24:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犹豫的言语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.18,0:24:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为想保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.13,0:00:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}不必消去这份记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}人生不是还很漫长？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:38.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}那些没有做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:42.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}只是想重新做起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:58.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}明明一直在追赶着梦的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:05.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}跌跌撞撞地走在弯曲的小道上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:08.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不奢望回到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}只是在苦寻那片丢失的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就像你明白一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:18.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}除去那像牺牲之后的悲伤表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:20.44,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}罪孽之后并不是泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}而是一直以来背负的苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.11,0:01:23.78,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}迷失在没有出口的情感迷宫中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:25.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在等待着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.45,0:01:27.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就像在白色笔记本上刻画一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:28.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}很想诚实地说出心声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.67,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}在逃避什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.67,0:01:32.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}…原来是叫做现实的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:35.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}为了实现愿望而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:39.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不禁想要大喊  你能听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:43.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}平安无事却让人没法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:45.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}…无家可归
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.95,0:01:49.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}感谢同伴们带来的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:51.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以要更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:54.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:57.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur6}这种痛苦也不赖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.13,0:00:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:33.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:38.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:44.22,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}约定和契约  被初夏的微风所怀抱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:48.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人互相依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:57.54,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在强颜欢笑的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:23:02.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}隐藏着逐渐扩大的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:12.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}所以  只装做没有发现  选择了重生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:21.69,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur6}在桌边继续等待那没有震撼的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:30.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur6}在空白的夜里  无法迎接的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:34.82,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}其实我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:40.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}那天看到的绯红天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.45,0:23:45.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}总有一天会想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:51.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6}抱着没有实现的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:55.47,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur6}两个人一起出发

